NAME
    The::Net -- Use the Net to fetch your required modules.

SYNOPSIS
        use The::Net;

        require 'http://www.example.com/Module.pm';

DESCRIPTION
    By using The::Net, you enable "require" to fetch Modules using HTTP or
    FTP, when given a URL as argument.

DEVELOPMENT
    The current sources of this module are found on github,
    <git://github.com/Abigail/the--net.git>.

